blogPost.excerpt:
So surreal to be uploading this video but here we are. 
If I missed anything in this video I'm sorry I felt like I was all over the place and couldn't remember half of what I wanted to say lol. I didn't do anything out of the ordinary to conceive. 

No videos of my reaction or J's, I just straight up told him after I shook the test for a solid 10 minutes. 😂
We didn't end up telling anyone this time until I was past 12 weeks. 

Thank you guys so much for all the encouraging words and congratulations. ❤️

We'll talk more in the upcoming vlogs.
